description:
This is a 7 minute workout called 'PERFECT 5 MIN CHEST WORKOUT | REAL RESULTS' from the channel THENX.
The workout falls under Strength/Calisthenics and Strength/Body weight.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Beginner fitness levels.
The workout has a The Firestarter and The Warrior Workout vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Moderate.

Original workout description: Follow along with Chris Heria as he takes you through a quick but effective 5 minute chest workout you can do several times through out the day, when ever you have time for some HUGE gains!
